HEADWORD: pachytene
<hw>pachytene</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Biol.)</fld> <def>The third stage
of the prophase of meiosis, the stage in which the pairing of homologous
chromosomes has been completed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

